    • Constructor Detail

      • Board

        public Board(java.lang.String s)
        Constructs a new board from given string. Use format "bR bN bB bQ bK bB bN bR\nbp\n## ## bp" where black pieces start with "b", white pieces start with "w", and rows are filled from left to right and ended at '\n'.
        Parameters:
        s - base string to construct the board from - empty for empty board
